        "synopsis": {
            "value": "At seven, Zhuo Yi Feng witnessed her parents' tragic deaths in a car accident, leading to selective amnesia. Raised by family friend Su Zi Jian, she assumes the identity of Su Nian Feng and grows up with his son, Su Mu Yun. Despite their strained relationship, Nian Feng is determined to apply for medical school, inspired by her friend Le Di Yin, who suffers from a mysterious illness. As secrets unravel and\n\nmisunderstandings surface, Nian Feng leaves home, seeking the truth about her past while navigating her dreams and complicated family dynamics.",
